      • save

        PointPermit save​(PointPermit pointPermit,
                 int empId,
                 int pointActionId)
        Saves or updates a given object with inserted parameters.
        Parameters:
        pointPermit - the object to save or update.
        empId - the employee's id, the employee will be inserted to the saved object's employee field.
        pointActionId - the point action's id, the point action will be inserted to the saved object's pointAction field.
        Returns:
        the saved or updated object, null - if there aren't updated object in the data base.
